# React

- Functional components only — no class components
- Hooks for state, effects, shared logic; custom hooks when shared
- Composition over inheritance; small focused components

## Practices (Clean Code, design patterns)

- **Clean Code**: clear names, single responsibility, no deep nesting, no duplicate logic
- **Design patterns**: when simplify design (container/presenter, strategy, factory) — not for pattern sake
- Thin UI; non-trivial logic in hooks or shared modules
- No god files: split by responsibility; one file ≠ unrelated features
